product_meta.title: Iams Proactive Health High Protein Adult Cat Food with Chicken & Salmon
product_meta.description: Flavor Name:Chicken & Salmon| Size:13 lb.Keep your cats at their best with IAMS High Protein Adult with Chicken & Salmon Dry Cat Food—a chicken-first recipe designed to give your active cats the protein-rich, flavorful food they naturally require. For outdoor or indoor cats, this cat kibble is made from high quality proteins like chicken and salmon (chicken is the #1 ingredient) for healthy vitality and healthy energy. Plus, its tailored fiber blend includes prebiotics and beet pulp to support your cat’s digestive health. If you’re looking for a high protein cat food with chicken or salmon, get your paws on this—and feed your cats’ carnivorous nature, keeping them ready to pounce, with IAMS High Protein Dry Cat Food.

High concentration of high quality protein helps maintain muscles and nourishes a healthy heart

This indoor or outdoor cat kibble includes calcium for strong teeth and healthy bones
